comments.body: The condition in the while loop for repositioning the button is incorrect and will never evaluate to true as intended. The vertical position check uses 'mouseY > y + EscapeButton.Bounds.Height / 2' which should likely be 'mouseY > y - EscapeButton.Bounds.Height / 2' to correctly check if the mouse is inside the button bounds vertically. Correcting this will prevent potential infinite loops and ensure proper button repositioning.
